   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Steps:\n",
    "\n",
    "* Choose the number of $k$\n",
    "* Select a distance metric\n",
    "* Find the k nearest neighbors of the sample\n",
    "* Assign the class label by majority vote\n",
    "\n"
   ]
